<h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">Reset Your Password</h2>

<p>Hi there,</p>

<p>Someone requested a link to reset your password. You can do this through the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
  <%= link_to 'Reset My Password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background-color: #8B4513; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;" %>
</div>

<div style="background: #fef3c7; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;">
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px;">
    <strong>Didn't request this?</strong> You can safely ignore this email. Your password won't change unless you click the button above.
  </p>
</div>

<p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">This link will expire in 6 hours.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 24px;">
  <strong>The Acer Coffee Team</strong>
</p>
